00:11:38.399 --> 00:11:38.679
Kumain pa.

00:11:38.679 --> 00:11:39.240
Hindi ako magpipigil.

00:11:39.240 --> 00:11:40.240
tatapusin ko lahat.

00:11:40.279 --> 00:11:41.080
Lahat, tingnan!

00:11:41.919 --> 00:11:43.440
Iyan ang
regalo ng Chinese New Year ni Young Master!

00:11:51.080 --> 00:11:52.200
Wow!

00:11:53.279 --> 00:11:54.519
ano yun?

00:11:54.679 --> 00:11:56.399
ang ganda!

00:11:57.039 --> 00:11:57.840
sa kanila,

00:11:57.960 --> 00:12:00.120
hindi ka
pa ba nagdiwang ng Chinese New Year's Eve?

00:12:00.120 --> 00:12:01.200
hindi,

00:12:01.240 --> 00:12:02.200
ito ang aking unang pagkakataon.

00:12:02.399 --> 00:12:03.399
Napakaganda nito!

00:12:10.600 --> 00:12:11.720
Napakasaya nito!

00:12:12.279 --> 00:12:13.759
Kawawang babae.

00:12:13.759 --> 00:12:15.759
Kahit kailan ay hindi pa siya nagkaroon
ng tamang Chinese New Year.

00:12:15.759 --> 00:12:16.519
sa kanila,

00:12:16.759 --> 00:12:17.960
ganito ang hitsura ng Bagong Taon.

00:12:18.159 --> 00:12:19.360
Mga fireworks yan.

00:12:20.200 --> 00:12:21.000
Ang ganda, di ba?

00:12:21.000 --> 00:12:21.919
Mga paputok.

00:12:22.879 --> 00:12:24.200
I bet they're powerful enough

00:12:24.200 --> 00:12:24.840
para ilabas

00:12:24.840 --> 00:12:26.159
ilang tao.

00:12:26.840 --> 00:12:29.519
Huwag magsabi ng malas
sa bisperas ng Chinese New Year!

00:12:29.799 --> 00:12:30.399
Oh, sige.

00:12:30.399 --> 00:12:31.279
Oh, itong babaeng ito...

00:12:31.879 --> 00:12:33.039
Tiyak na sinasabi niya ang kanyang isip.

00:12:36.559 --> 00:12:37.200
Halika.

00:12:37.200 --> 00:12:38.250
Magbuhos ng ilang alak para sa Guro.

00:12:39.360 --> 00:12:40.240
Sige.

00:12:40.879 --> 00:12:41.679
Dito.

00:12:42.960 --> 00:12:43.759
ano?

00:12:44.559 --> 00:12:45.360
gusto kong ipakita sayo

00:12:45.399 --> 00:12:46.279
ilang iba't ibang mga paputok.

00:12:46.279 --> 00:12:47.000
meron pa?

00:12:52.879 --> 00:12:54.000
Ito ay mga paputok din?

00:12:55.519 --> 00:12:56.320
Heto, kunin mo ang mga ito.

00:13:06.360 --> 00:13:07.559
Ito ay napaka-cool!

00:13:07.710 --> 00:13:08.240
Shen Wangchen!

00:13:08.240 --> 00:13:09.279
Tingnan mo!

00:13:20.550 --> 00:13:24.487
♪Pagmasdan ang liwanag ng buwan kasama ka♪

00:13:25.937 --> 00:13:29.612
♪Sa huli, magkahiwalay tayo ng landas♪

00:13:30.679 --> 00:13:31.720
Ang saya, di ba?

00:13:31.720 --> 00:13:32.480
Ay, sorry.

00:13:32.480 --> 00:13:33.360
Samahan mo kami!

00:13:33.510 --> 00:13:34.300
Sama-sama tayong magsaya!

00:13:34.679 --> 00:13:35.360
Ang saya mo dito.

00:13:35.360 --> 00:13:36.240
Huwag kang mag-alala sa amin.

00:13:36.240 --> 00:13:37.360
Sige.

00:13:38.279 --> 00:13:39.080
Batang Madam!

00:13:40.240 --> 00:13:41.120
Bumalik ka, Mr. Zhen!

00:13:41.120 --> 00:13:42.159
Ito ay masaya!

00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:43.399
Mr. Zhen!

00:13:43.799 --> 00:13:45.480
Huwag mo akong takutin, Young Madam!

00:13:45.480 --> 00:13:47.093
♪Sino ang kasama ko sa aking mahabang paglalakbay?♪

00:13:47.237 --> 00:13:51.900
♪Saan ako makakapagpahinga
